snippet.title: Ashes of Creation - Kickstarter Video
snippet.description:
Ashes of Creation is LIVE on Kickstarter! 
Join our community and breathe life into Ashes of Creation by pledging your support for our project.

Kickstarter - https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1791529601/ashes-of-creation-new-mmorpg-by-intrepid-studios/description

Sign up today and participate in developer discussions, and enter to win weekly drawings for Pre-Alpha Testing

Official Ashes of Creation Website - http://www.ashesofcreation.com/


Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/AshesofCreation

Twitter - https://twitter.com/MediaAoC

Discord - http://www.Discord.gg/AshesofCreation
